title: Poland recalls ambassador to Israel indefinitely as restitution row deepens - Reuters
description: Poland's ambassador to Israel has been recalled until further notice, the foreign ministry said on Monday, in a further sign of the deteriorating relations between the countries after Warsaw introduced a law affecting World War Two property restitution.
